BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:First Thursdays Festival\, with entertainment on the main stage by
  Soul Revue\, Eleanor & Dario\, Jacobs Saxophone Ensemble\, IU Musical The
 atre\, and InMotion Dance Company
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260402T160000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260402T190000
UID:ai1ec-147604-94476@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:First Thursdays showcase the diversity of arts and humanities
  at IU Bloomington and offer a welcoming environment for students\, facul
 ty\, staff\, and community members to explore new creative outlets. Each 
 event is a unique opportunity to experience the wonderful work of artists\
 , performers\, and scholars from all across campus and around town.The Ap
 ril First Thursdays will be a festival of art\, ideas\, and community feat
 uring 2 performance stages\, 80+ activity booths\, 20+ arts vendors\, food
  trucks\, giveaways\, and more. Around the IU Fine Arts Plaza\, there will
  be a 1776 Trail\, poster printing\, 3D fabrication demos\, and henna tatt
 ooing among many other activities. On the main stage\, we’ll have perfor
 mances by Soul Revue\, Eleanor & Dario\, Jacobs Saxophone Ensemble\, IU Mu
 sical Theatre\, and InMotion Dance Company. For more details\, visitgo.iu.
 edu/first-thursdays.
LOCATION:IU Fine Arts Plaza\, 1201 E 7th St\, Bloomington
URL:https://wfhb.org/event/first-thursdays-festival/?instance_id=94476
X-SOURCE:WFHB Community Calendar
END:VEVENT
