 harisma. Fearless and unabashed\, Gauri draws endless material from her cu
 ltural background\, as well as politics\, society\, and everyday chaos\, c
 rafting sharp jokes into her pointed stand-up routines. And when it comes 
 to crowd work and interacting with the audience\, she is undoubtedly in a 
 league of her own. This show is for fans of stand-up that goes beyond the 
 trivial.
LOCATION:The Comedy Attic\, 123 South Walnut\, corner of 4th and Walnut\,B
 loomington
URL:https://wfhb.org/event/the-bloomington-debut-of-gauri-b-shows-at-700-a
 nd-915/?instance_id=94467
X-SOURCE:WFHB Community Calendar
END:VEVENT
