 up. As he prepares to join the fearsome Shark Guard\, Finn can’t shake t
 he feeling that he’s different from the other sharks. Deep inside\, he d
 iscovers a colorful fish inside him—a part of himself that longs to spar
 kle\, sing\, and dance. As Finn embarks on a journey of self-discovery\, f
 riendship\, and adventure\, he finds the courage to be himself! Fun for al
 l ages!PB&J Cafe: A Dinner Theater for Kids! At the PB&J Cafe\, young thea
 tergoers will enjoy a meal during the performance and leave with autograph
 s from their favorite characters.
LOCATION:Waldron Arts Center. 122 S. Walnut Street\, Bloomington
URL:https://wfhb.org/event/finn-a-new-musical-a-sensory-friendly-performan
 ce-at-the-pbj-cafe/?instance_id=90740
X-SOURCE:WFHB Community Calendar
END:VEVENT
